data.description: Beautifully remodeled throughout, move-in ready 3/4 Bedrooms, 1.5 baths.  Large backyard has awesome view of Fox Run Park complete with baseball field, trees & large playset!  Gorgeous kitchen with quartz countertops, tile backsplash, accent lighting, brand new stainless steel appliances all included!  Full bath has skylight for natural light, LVP flooring throughout.  Lower level could be used as a 4th bedroom or family room, oversized 1 car garage w/large work bench, shelving, whole house ventilation fan, 2 tiered deck, storage shed, washer & dryer included!  1 Year home warranty.  Must see!
